      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Guide"><a href="#Guide" class="headerlink" title="Guide"></a>Guide</h2><h3 id="Create-a-folder-eg"><a href="#Create-a-folder-eg" class="headerlink" title="Create a folder, eg. "></a>Create a folder, eg. <figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![](nodejs-express-simple/create-folder.png)&#10;&#10;### Enter folder ```server``` and install express&#10;```shell&#10;npm install express --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h3><p><img src="nodejs-express-simple/express-installed.png" alt=""></p>
